{
  "stem": "11723.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And by the way, a little note here of my own.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I, as a little child, I could never understand why we were always called [NON-ENGLISH], which means stinking Jew.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not until this year did I understand where this come from.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I read a book called And in that book, they tell the entire history-- the author tells the entire history of anti-Semitism, how it developed from the time of Christ on.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in the Middle Ages, he says, Jews were supposed to be identified with the devil.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, well, we talk about the devil now, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The devil here and the devil take you and what have you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The devil made me do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But in the Middle Ages, the devil was like a real thing in, in, in the lives of people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they considered a Jew to be the embodiment of the devil.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now the devil's supposed to have emitted this sulfuric smell.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the Jews, because they were supposed to have been the incarnation of the devil, they were also supposed to have been emitting this sulfuric, sulfuric smell.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that's how, from generation to generation, it came down 'stinking Jew.' And I could never understand why, when my family was cleaner and more hygienic, that most of those people who called us stinking Jew.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Well, that's just an aside, you know, from a child's point of view.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Anyways, when we went back to Budapest-- now, this was end of March or so-- at that point, my family knew that something has to be done.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they were thinking of going anywhere, but nobody wanted us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My mother actually had a passport to come to this country.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Well, she applied to come to this country.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She had a passport.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She couldn't get a visa.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
